<?xml version="1.0"?><?mso-application progid="Excel.Sheet"?><Workbook xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:spreadsheet" xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" xmlns:x="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel" xmlns:ss="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:spreadsheet" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40"><DocumentProperties xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office"><LastAuthor>Luis Ferreira</LastAuthor><LastSaved>2020-02-06T13:49:13Z</LastSaved><Version>16.00</Version></DocumentProperties><OfficeDocumentSettings xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office"><AllowPNG/></OfficeDocumentSettings><ExcelWorkbook xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel"><WindowHeight>7830</WindowHeight><WindowWidth>16170</WindowWidth><WindowTopX>32767</WindowTopX><WindowTopY>32767</WindowTopY><RefModeR1C1/><ProtectStructure>False</ProtectStructure><ProtectWindows>False</ProtectWindows></ExcelWorkbook><Styles><Style ss:ID="Default" ss:Name="Normal"><Alignment ss:Vertical="Bottom"/><Borders/><Font ss:FontName="Calibri" x:Family="Swiss" ss:Size="11" ss:Color="#000000"/><Interior/><NumberFormat/><Protection/></Style><Style ss:ID="s62"><Alignment ss:Vertical="Top" ss:WrapText="1"/></Style></Styles><Worksheet ss:Name="Script"><Table x:FullColumns="1" x:FullRows="1" ss:StyleID="s62" ss:DefaultColumnWidth="239.25" ss:DefaultRowHeight="15"><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="120"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SOUND_UNITMODS</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Anything between straight brackets - i.e. [ ] - is a formatting tag. Do not change these tags and keep them in the same relative position in the text. Anything between curly brackets - i.e. { } - is a place where text or numbers will be inserted by the game. Do not change the tag, but feel free to change its position in the text to suit the localized text.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SCENE ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZATION NOTES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SOUND_MOD_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Deafening Amplifiers</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ogłuszające wzmacniacze</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="135"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SOUND_MOD_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit's Sonic weapons have a {Disorientedchance}[strengthPhysical/] strength chance ({DisorientedRepeatingChance}[strengthPhysical/] for repeating attacks) to apply [abilityred]Disoriented[/abilityred] to non-Ethereal units, giving the unit a {FumbleChance}% fumble chance to its attacks, for {Duration}[turn/].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Broń dźwiękowa tej jednostki ma szansę o sile {Disorientedchance}[strengthPhysical/] ({DisorientedRepeatingChance}[strengthPhysical/] dla ataków wielokrotnych) wywołania [abilityred]dezorientacji[/abilityred] u jednostek organicznych i cyborgów, co powoduje {FumbleChance}% szansy na pudło ich ataków przez {Duration}[turn/].</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Disoriented is a Status Effect in StatusEffects_UnitProperties_DLC04</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SOUND_MOD_2</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Focused Sonolysis Module</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Moduł skoncentrowanej sonolizy</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SOUND_MOD_2</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit's Sonic weapons gain [abilityred]Armor Melt[/abilityred], destroying {ArmorAmount}[armor/] per hit.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Broń dźwiękowa tej jednostki zyskuje [abilityred]stopienie pancerza[/abilityred], niszczące {ArmorAmount}[armor/] na trafienie.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Armor Melt is a Status Effect in StatusEffects_UnitProperties, in the base game.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SOUND_MOD_3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Acute Pitch</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Agresywna tonacja</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="120"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SOUND_MOD_3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit's Sonic attacks gain a {StrengthChance}[strengthPhysical/] strength chance ({StrengthChanceRepeating}[strengthPhysical/] for repeating attacks) to apply [abilityred]Resonance[/abilityred], reducing their[damagePhysical/] resistance for {Duration}[turn/].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ataki dźwiękowe tej jednostki uzyskują szansę (siła {StrengthChance}[strengthPhysical/], {StrengthChanceRepeating}[strengthPhysical/] dla ataków wielokrotnych) na spowodowanie [abilityred]rezonansu[/abilityred], zmniejszającego odporność[damagePhysical/] na {Duration}[turn/].</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Resonance is a Status Effect in StatusEffects_UnitProperties_DLC04</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SOUND_MOD_4</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Reverbing Shields</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Tarcza pogłosowa</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="150"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SOUND_MOD_4</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit gains {Resistance}[DefensePhysical/].[br/]In addition, attacks on this unit have a {StrengthChance}[strengthPhysical/] strength chance of applying a stack of [abilityred]Reverb[/abilityred] to the attacker, which deals {DamageAmount}[damagePhysical/] damage to the unit and its adjacent allies when it reaches {StackAmount} stacks. On failure, applies [abilityred]Resonance[/abilityred] instead.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ta jednostka zyskuje {Resistance}[DefensePhysical/].[br/]Dodatkowo skierowane na nią ataki mają szansę o sile {StrengthChance}[strengthPhysical/] spowodowania [abilityred]pogłosu[/abilityred] u napastnika, co zadaje {DamageAmount}[damagePhysical/] pkt. obrażeń jednostce i sąsiadującym z nią sprzymierzeńcom, gdy osiągnie {StackAmount}. poziom. W razie niepowodzenia wywołuje [abilityred]rezonans[/abilityred].</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Reverb is a Status Effect in StatusEffects_UnitProperties_DLC04</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SOUND_MOD_5</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Cavitation Module</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Moduł kawitacyjny</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="150"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SOUND_MOD_5</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit's Sonic weapons apply [abilityred]Reverb[/abilityred] ({ReverbRepeatingChance}[strengthPhysical/] strength chance for repeating attacks) to units, a stacking effect that deals {DamageAmount}[damagePhysical/] damage to the unit and its adjacent allies when it reaches {StackAmount} stacks.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Broń dźwiękowa tej jednostki wywołuje [abilityred]pogłos[/abilityred] u celu (szansa o sile {ReverbRepeatingChance}[strengthPhysical/] dla ataków wielokrotnych). Jest to kumulujący się efekt, który zadaje {DamageAmount}[damagePhysical/] pkt. obrażeń trafionej jednostce i sąsiadującym z nią sprzymierzeńcom, gdy osiągnie {StackAmount}. poziom.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Reverb is a Status Effect in StatusEffects_UnitProperties_DLC04</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SOUND_MOD_6</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sono-Interference Module</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Moduł interferencyjny</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="135"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SOUND_MOD_6</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit's Sonic weapons have a {ImpairedChance}[strengthPhysical/] strength chance ({ImpairedRepeatingChance}[strengthPhysical/] for repeating attacks) to apply [abilityred]Impaired[/abilityred] to units, disabling their mods and applying [abilityred]Slow[/abilityred]. On failure, only applies [abilityred]Slow[/abilityred].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Broń dźwiękowa tej jednostki ma szansę o sile {ImpairedChance}[strengthPhysical/] ({ImpairedRepeatingChance}[strengthPhysical/] dla ataków wielokrotnych) spowodowania [abilityred]osłabienia[/abilityred] u celu, co wyłączy jego modyfikacje i wywoła [abilityred]spowolnienie[/abilityred]. W razie niepowodzenia powoduje tylko [abilityred]spowolnienie[/abilityred].</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Impaired is a Status Effect in StatusEffects_UnitProperties_DLC04</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MOD_1_TEMPLATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Blaring</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ryk</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MOD_1_TEMPLATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME2</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Noisy</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Hałaśliwość</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MOD_1_TEMPLATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ringing</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Dźwięczność</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MOD_1_TEMPLATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME4</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Roaring</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wrzaskliwość</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MOD_1_TEMPLATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME5</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Thunderous</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gromkość</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MOD_1_TEMPLATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME6</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Rowdy</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Krzykliwość</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MOD_2_TEMPLATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Destructive</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Destrukcyjność</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MOD_2_TEMPLATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME2</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Crushing</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zmiażdżenie</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MOD_2_TEMPLATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Razing</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Burzenie</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MOD_2_TEMPLATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME4</Data></Cell><Cell><D